.TH PRODBOX_k8s 1
.SH NAME
prodbox-k8s \- Kubernetes helpers
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B prodbox k8s
.SH DESCRIPTION
Kubernetes health and log utilities.
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
\fBhealth\fR
Check cluster health
.TP
\fBwait\fR
Wait for deployments to be ready
.TP
\fBlogs\fR
Show recent infrastructure logs
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
\fBprodbox k8s health\fR
Check Kubernetes health.
